graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Operator"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Deployment]
        Webhook[Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Controller -->|validates via| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Model Serving Runtime Pod"
        direction TB
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Container<br/>Model routing/caching]
        RuntimeAdapter[Runtime Adapter<br/>gRPC bridge]
        StorageHelper[Storage Helper<br/>Model puller]
        ModelRuntime[Model Runtime<br/>Triton/MLServer/OpenVINO]
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP]

        ModelMesh -->|8085/TCP gRPC| RuntimeAdapter
        RuntimeAdapter -->|8001/TCP gRPC| ModelRuntime
        StorageHelper -->|coordinates| ModelMesh
        RESTProxy -->|translates to gRPC| ModelMesh
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        PredictorCR[Predictor CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ClusterServingRuntimeCR[ClusterServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
    end

    User[User/Dashboard] -->|creates| PredictorCR
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR

    PredictorCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ClusterServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates/manages| ModelMesh
    Controller -->|configures| RuntimeAdapter

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        etcd[etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+]
        S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        CertManager[cert-manager<br/>TLS certs]
    end

    Controller -->|state management| etcd
    StorageHelper -->|retrieves models| S3
    Controller -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus
    Webhook -->|TLS cert| CertManager

    subgraph "Optional Integrations"
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio<br/>mTLS enforcement]
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web UI]
    end

    ModelMesh -.->|optional mTLS| ServiceMesh
    Dashboard -->|manages via K8s API| Controller

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2
    style ModelMesh fill:#7ed321
    style RuntimeAdapter fill:#7ed321
    style StorageHelper fill:#7ed321
    style ModelRuntime fill:#7ed321
    style RESTProxy fill:#7ed321
    style PredictorCR fill:#f5a623
    style ServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623
    style ClusterServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623
    style InferenceServiceCR fill:#f5a623
    style etcd fill:#e8e8e8
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8
    style CertManager fill:#e8e8e8
    style ServiceMesh fill:#d3d3d3
    style Dashboard fill:#d3d3d3
